https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/1tt5Rxl7OdfflUj06c0Ft0G8tki.jpg "Ao Vivo em Goiânia" is the fourth DVD of the Brazilian musical group Banda Calypso, recorded in Goiânia on October 5th and 6th, 2007, it brings a show full of new songs, with only 4 songs already known. It was released in November of the same year. It brought a different show full of musical influences, and a participation of the duo of composers, Edu & Maraial (Edú Luppa and Marquinhos Maraial).
